WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:10.148
IEFP CRM is a teaching platform that brings together, in one place, everything taught in the CRM and data-protection training units.

00:00:10.148 --> 00:00:13.607
The Dashboard shows the business at a glance.

00:00:13.607 --> 00:00:18.528
Proposals live in a visual pipeline, with PDF and email sending.

00:00:18.528 --> 00:00:22.371
In Analytics you follow the funnel and conversion.

00:00:22.371 --> 00:00:25.523
The GDPR module brings compliance to life

00:00:25.523 --> 00:00:27.983
consents, requests and breaches.

00:00:27.983 --> 00:00:31.289
And every contact has a 360-degree profile.

00:00:31.289 --> 00:00:35.210
All with Portuguese sample data, ready to practise.
